# Privacy-Preserving Record Linkage (PPRL) — COMP3850 Group 52

Industry capstone for Dinusha Vatsalan & Piyumi Seneviratne, Macquarie University.
Comparison of five record-linkage models under Bloom-filter encoding and differential privacy.

## Overview
Encodes quasi-identifiers into Bloom filters / Counting Bloom Filters (q-grams), applies
bit-level differential privacy (bit-flipping) at epsilon ∈ {2, 3, 4}, blocks records, and
classifies pairs as match / non-match using five models: threshold baseline, Logistic
Regression, Random Forest, SVM and KNN. Evaluated with F1, precision and recall.

